            <title>Mobile lubrication system now available</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;a href="http://www.wastequip-cusco.com"&gt;Cusco&lt;/a&gt;, a company operating under &lt;a href="http://www.wastequip.com" target="_blank"&gt;Wastequip&lt;/a&gt;, has introduced its mobile lubrication and waste fluid retrieval systems for servicing mobile equipment. The systems allow for servicing in the field when time does not allow for the return of equipment back to fixed service locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The mobile units are equipped with seven different fluid delivery systems, along with a grease-dispensing system, a waste fluid recovery system and compressed air.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Typical applications include mining operations, oil field sites, forestry, construction sites and any company with fleets of equipment that may require servicing while in the field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&amp;ldquo;Cusco&amp;rsquo;s mobile lubrication and waste fluid retrieval systems are ideal for everything from changing the fluid on an excavator in the field to changing a tire on a truck on the side of the road,&amp;rdquo; says Steve Godwin, president, Cusco. &amp;ldquo;Best of all, these systems are designed to perform in the most demanding weather conditions.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
