	[6] T. Andersson. Endurance testing in theory. Ball Bearing Journal, 217:14&amp;ndash;23, 1983.&lt;br /&gt;
	[7] D. Meijer, D. Polymer thickened lubricating grease. European Patent Application (EP 0 700 986 A3), 1996.&lt;br /&gt;
	[8] SKF General Catalog, 6000/I (2008)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/preventive_maintenance/~4/0oRPNc2mTdk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-10-21T14:03:22-05:00</a10:updated>
