            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:e8fc0b40-3a45-41f8-9b36-9dd4014bd31f</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/preventive_maintenance/~3/3Je3jEPcgTw/italian-power-plant-filter-strategy</link>
